# Rust build artifacts
target/
**/target/

# Native libs are produced by `native/build.{ps1,sh}` and copied into
# app/src/main/jniLibs/ — they're build outputs, not source.
# (The jniLibs entries below are scoped to *only* the rosenpass library
# so other prebuilt .so files like libwg.so / libsentry.so stay tracked.)
/app/src/main/jniLibs/arm64-v8a/librosenpass_jni.so
/app/src/main/jniLibs/armeabi-v7a/librosenpass_jni.so
/app/src/main/jniLibs/x86_64/librosenpass_jni.so

# cargo-ndk leaves these behind
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak
